## Hub and spoke (HARD)

- **Matt ‚Üî orchestrator only.** Teammates do not own the user relationship.
- **Teammates report back to the orchestrator** ‚Äî outcome, evidence, blockers, file list, oracle result. Orchestrator synthesizes for Matt.
- **Teammates ask the orchestrator** when something is missing, ambiguous, or unknown. They do **not** invent requirements, redefine the product, or ‚Äúuse sensible defaults‚Äù across a comprehension fork.
- **Orchestrator asks Matt** for taste / risk / credentials / real scope ambiguity (conduct clarify-first). Never launder Matt-questions into silent worker defaults.
